Package: pbdIO
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2016-02-23
Title: Programming with Big Data -- Input-Output
Authors@R: c(person("George", "Ostrouchov", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
        "ostrouchovg@ornl.gov"),
        person("George", "Ostrouchov", role = "aut"),
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), pbdMPI
Enhances: pbdNCDF4, pbdADIOS
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Description: An interface to parallel input output packages
        with a focus on Single Program/Multiple Data ('SPMD')
        parallel programming style, which is intended for batch parallel
        execution.
SystemRequirements: OpenMPI (>= 1.5.4) on Solaris, Linux, Mac, and
        FreeBSD. MS-MPI (Microsoft HPC Pack 2012 R2 MS-MPI
        Redistributable Package) on Windows.
License: Mozilla Public License 2.0
URL: http://r-pbd.org/
BugReports: http://group.r-pbd.org/
MailingList: Please send questions and comments regarding pbdR to
        RBigData@gmail.com
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged:
Author: George Ostrouchov [aut, cre]
Maintainer: George Ostrouchov <ostrouchovg@ornl.gov>
